{"tid":1651243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【和你Thank】感謝前線消防活動 #ThankYouHKFirefighters","createTime":"2019-10-13T09:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T15:52:24.000Z","uid":299387,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7b70dcd9551ce94a736b88e209b0a72914bbec","tid":1651243,"uid":299387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"首先，我明白大家對消防有不同意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個社會幾百萬人，無可能所有人都持相同諗法，如果你覺得支持消防有問題，請你出返去推行動post。<br />\n<br />\n行動係非常重要，但我希望所有市民都可以係唔駛行動既日子參與下做啲野<br />\n做和理非活動 =/= 有行動唔上街，兩者唔係對立<br />\n<br />\n<ins>活動目的</ins><br />\n- 向前線消防/救護表達謝意 （啲高層明顯係藍，食屎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但前線消防又出片又出文去支持我地，我地點可以連多謝都無句）<br />\n- 比外媒從另一個角度去分析「點解同為紀錄部隊，香港人對消防/ 救護既態度好咁多」，示威活動報導左咁多日，不如我地比啲新方向佢地<br />\n- 「感謝」乃為正面既活動，可以用作文宣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>活動內容</ins><br />\n- 於任何social media上載一張同感謝消防/救護有關既相片，並hashtag <span style=\"color: red;\">#ThankYouHKFirefighters</span> / <span style=\"color: red;\">#HongKongFirefighters</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>相片idea</ins><br />\n- 文宣圖 （屌黑警文宣好重要，但唔好忘記正面文宣都好緊要）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8npCixU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8npCixU.jpg&h=298b757b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或者用返呢位消防員既手繪圖 - <a href=\"https://bit.ly/32ckBGi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32ckBGi&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=0ae09d79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/32ckBGi</a><br />\n【漫畫家分享】消防員手繪畫寄語年輕人珍惜生命！「唔會畀佢哋單獨一個面對」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dfy7FJ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDfy7FJ3.jpg&h=c85586ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 用Canva DIY整都好簡單<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SXn4H9d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSXn4H9d.png&h=224eae88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 自己/ 搵小朋友畫一幅畫，寫句多謝消防/ 救護哥哥姐姐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j9NwnYB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj9NwnYB.png&h=82092b53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 戴頭盔/ 同街井合照對消防黎講都會有共鳴<br />\n（唔想自爆就唔好出樣，到今日都未識保護自己我都唔知可以點幫你）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aqh4H07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAqh4H07.jpg&h=74d3f8d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 以消防車既顏色為方向自由發揮（紅底黃間）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKtod7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKtod7K.jpg&h=7fd17cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果今次活動反應唔錯，我地下次可以搞多謝傳媒，多謝First Aid之類。勝利之日，我地仲要多謝自己 - 每一個有份參與過呢場運動既真香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界我地都多謝，淨係屌打黑警你班仆街，吹咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n不篤灰 不分化 贏就一齊贏 <br />\n不麻木 不忘記 要撐到煲底相見之日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad2a09d4f59319772fec4278e586a4ca2691935","tid":1651243,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700d505f0a242c7109c428ee30b7ea94f34a34dc","tid":1651243,"uid":80277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:37:46.000Z","msg":"[即時] RTHK直播 TM 有架康文署貨van有狗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1650940/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1650940/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n卧狗係新都會優品360捉手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1650958/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1650958/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/pwbJYZ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2FpwbJYZ.jpeg&h=fea4b22a&s={SI